png", "id": "1050200259945411", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001705_1050200263278744_2536765123562298486_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6AMWusshhPoQ7kNvgEm4uzK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCOV5t6WhVfZqD5qt3d4WwQjn3l01N_OhHOM2FqhpbLSg&oe=67373ECB"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Level - Tilted 2560x1440.png", "id": "1253462735677317", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974547_1253462742343983_8818318723270229370_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5TCu57zzFHcQ7kNvgGWU6RB&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC1Q-b_9-hdI1U4UNp-7bo1vw-0VE2Y2cOs1R7pBbiSdw&oe=67371E20"}, "display_name": "Close Encounters Demo", "keywords": ["UFO", "Paddle", "Ball", "Space"], "long_description": "VRelity Review: \"25 Best games in VR for Meta Quest 3 and Quest 2 that you have to play.\"\n\nUse your controller thumb sticks to deflect one or more balls to targets for collection.\n\nEach planet presents a challenging array of targets that must be collected to the waiting UFO above.\n\nPower-ups become available to assist in the collection process:\n- Extra Ball = Additional ball added to total balls available\n- Multi-Ball = Additional ball launched at location of power up\n- Power Ball = Blows through targets.  Lasts for 30 seconds.\n- Extra Time = Adds 60 to level timer\n\nBall speed increases and paddle size decreases as you progress through each challenge.\n\nTimed Demo Version: Play specific levels for about 60 seconds to get a feel for this game.\n", "short_description": "Lightning-fast reflexes are required to collect samples from each world and upload them to the hovering UFO.\n\nVRelity Review: \"25 Best games in VR for Meta Quest 3 and Quest 2 that you have to play.\"\n\nTimed Demo Version of \"Close Encounters\"."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.abbynormalproductions.net/priv